的一些无名 iPad 保护套贵，但如果您想要在保护和风格之间取得完美平衡，它们是值得的。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>说到填满亚马逊搜索结果页面的更便宜的 iPad 保护套，一些真正物有所值的保护套来自<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9zdG9yZXMvcGFnZS80QzAxQTE0QS0yMDY3LTQ2NTYtOUY1MS05NzBCRkEzRkZFNkQ_aW5ncmVzcz0yJnZpc2l0SWQ9Y2I0OGEwYWYtNWE3NC00MjgxLTk4YTAtOGRjZDk3ODNiNDRjJnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWV6LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI5NGY3ZTBhNC0yYzM3LTM3ZmQtOTg3OS03MzkxNzdjY2JmNGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQBVtR1yUWDA4KH3DEAnuwYlH1Lii5ZqmRzj8xCQKGOm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fpage%2F4C01A14A-2067-4656-9F51-970BFA3FFE6D%3Fingress%3D2%26visitId%3Dcb48a0af-5a74-4281-98a0-8dcd9783b44c%26">Moko</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9zdG9yZXMvcGFnZS8xRTJFOEQ1Ni05QjMzLTRDNkItQkExMS01NDc0NkE3NTczMEM_aW5ncmVzcz0yJnZpc2l0SWQ9OTQxODA2YWEtMTgyNS00M2M4LTg0MDYtMGMyNjFkNGY4OTA1JnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWV6LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI5NGY3ZTBhNC0yYzM3LTM3ZmQtOTg3OS03MzkxNzdjY2JmNGMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQJT2WbeHZeHbxJCp4-_Nt_VqYr8morUoNTzMrg2Wmo1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fpage%2F1E2E8D56-9B33-4C6B-BA11-54746A75730C%3Fingress%3D2%26visitId%3D941806aa-1825-43c8-8406-0c261d4f8905%26">ProCase</a> 。如果您喜欢 Apple Smart Cover 的外观和感觉，但又不想花 50 多美元购买一个，那么这两个品牌都有仿制品，